      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im having a really hard time sleeping lately. like i can't shut my brain off at all. im already taking some melatonin every night but it barely does anything. my doctor gave me some zolpidem (ambien) to help but i was thinking of maybe taking the melatonin and the zolpidem together to make sure it actually works? is that safe to do for a stronger effect?",
