      "content": "i get that, but i already asked the doc and they were kinda vague about supplements. i'm just really desperate cuz i'm exhausted at work. like, if i just take a small dose of the melatonin along with my ambien, is it really gonna be that much of a big deal? i don't feel like i'd get \"dangerously\" sleepy, just more tired so i can actually pass out.",
